{{Infobox football biography | name=Pedro Gonçalves | fullname=Pedro António Pereira Gonçalves | birth_date={{birth date and age|1998|6|28|df=y}} | birth_place=[[Chaves, Portugal|Chaves]], Portugal | height={{convert|1.73|m|abbr=on}} | position=[[Midfielder]] | currentclub=[[Wolverhampton Wanderers F.C.|Wolverhampton Wanderers]] | clubnumber= | youthyears1= | youthclubs1=[[G.D. Chaves|Chaves]] | youthyears2= | youthclubs2=[[S.C. Braga|Braga]] | youthyears3= | youthclubs3=[[Valencia CF|Valencia]] | youthyears4=2017–2018 | youthclubs4=[[Wolverhampton Wanderers F.C.|Wolverhampton Wanderers]] | years1=2018– | clubs1=[[Wolverhampton Wanderers F.C.|Wolverhampton Wanderers]] | caps1=0 | goals1=0 | pcupdate=28 August 2018 }} '''Pedro António Pereira Gonçalves''' (born 28 June 1998), also known as '''Pote''', is a Portuguese [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[midfielder]]. He is signed to [[Premier League]] side [[Wolverhampton Wanderers F.C.|Wolverhampton Wanderers]].
==Career== Gonçalves joined English club [[Wolverhampton Wanderers F.C.|Wolverhampton Wanderers]] in July 2017, initially on a one-year-deal.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.expressandstar.com/sport/football/wolverhampton-wanderers-fc/2017/07/18/wolves-snap-up-two-portuguese-youngsters/|title=Wolves snap up two Portuguese youngsters|publisher=Express & Star|date=18 July 2017}}</ref>
The midfielder made his professional club debut on 28 August 2018 in a 2–0 League Cup victory at [[Sheffield Wednesday F.C.|Sheffield Wednesday]].<ref>{{cite news| title=Sheffield Wednesday v Wolves|publisher=BBC Sport| url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/45254598| date=28 August 2018}}</ref>
